<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The threat of big job losses for its 30,000 em=
ployees raised the stakes, according to people on the Feb. 3 conference cal=
l, who declined to be named. Kirkland &amp; Ellis attorney Joshua Sussberg =
reminded lenders of the human cost should the firm crater before all capita=
